-- SandRidge Energy to Buy Dynamic Offshore
-- B y   T i n a   D a v i s
-- 2012-02-01T21:11:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-01/sandridge-energy-to-buy-dynamic-offshore.html
SandRidge Energy Inc. (SD)  agreed to buy
Dynamic Offshore Resources LLC for $1.28 billion in cash and
stock.  The purchase consists of $680 million in cash and about 74
million shares of SandRidge, the company said in a statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tina Davis at 
 tinadavis@bloomberg.net  